{"about_the_game":"<i>Are you ready to become Dr. Alb's Prodigy? Embark on an epic journey in a post-apocalyptic universe, where you must aid the Doctor in battling invaders, rescuing stranded characters, and uncovering the root of the looming danger.</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727890/extras/AboutFeatures.png?t=1737982475\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Pixel art with modern visual effects<br></li><li> Turn based and real time action<br></li><li> Unique roguelike runs</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Combining old and new</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727890/extras/DoggoWalk2_2.gif?t=1737982475\" /><br>Pixel graphics set within a 3D environment featuring cool lighting and impressive<br>visual effects.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Multi-layered combat system</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727890/extras/BattleScene2_5.gif?t=1737982475\" /><br>The combat system blends turn-based and real-time mechanics, depending on<br>enemy encounters and your damage capabilities.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Side quests and intriguing characters to meet</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727890/extras/UniqueNPC.gif?t=1737982475\" /><br>You'll engage with diverse NPCs and have the opportunity to undertake various<br>side missions.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Roguelike elements and procedural generation</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727890/extras/LootGrabG.gif?t=1737982475\" /><br>Embark on unique roguelike runs featuring randomized levels and elements, as you<br>enhance your character with unique loot and abilities.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/ap